history.text: Hello
Have you seen the movie Batman vs Superman?
Hello, No, I have not. Have You?
Yes, I saw it in theaters. It was pretty good.
Are you into Batman at all?
I have seen a few trailers and I would like to see it, but a little on the fence. Who are the actors in it?
My grandson really likes those kind of movies.
It has Ben Affleck as Batman, and Henry Cavill as Superman from the other two he played in. I forget who plays Wonder Woman in it, but it's the same lady as Wonder Woman and Justice League.
It also has Jesse Eisenberg as Luther.
I always thought Batman and Superman were friends?
That is a pretty good cast.
This movie has a different spin on when they first met, if you've seen Man of Steel where the town is nearly destroyed Batman feels he is a threat.
They eventually do become friends though.
I am still a little iffy on the new Wonder Woman. She is really different from the one I remember.
I didn't see that one.
I'm not a huge fan of the Wonder Woman movie itself, but they did a good job with her in the Justice League movie.

I'm iffy as well 
on the whole backstory and the way they did her in her own movie.
I am glad they do become friends
She is very different.
I did like the Justice League, but haven't seen the Wonder Woman movie, yet.
She is different. Almost so different they should have made up a whole new character for her.
Justice League is much better of the two. It can be a bit confusing watching without having seen Batman V Superman, since it shows how he was dead.
Very true. They tried to create an entire new image for her but keep the same name.
Is it Super Girl that was a TV show for a while?
Yes, on the CW.
They mixed it with Arrow and the Flash for a lot of crossovers
I don't know how well that did but I do enjoy these movies with a variety of different super powered people, like, "Gifted."
There is quite a few now.
Yeah, without being too over the top. Marvel does a good job with them as well.
Like Daredevil on Netflix is pretty good.
I am really curious about the Batman -vs- Superman movie now
It's definetly worth checking out.
I hope you enjoy it if you happen to check it out.
I haven't seen that either, but will check it out. I have been looking for something new to watch.
There are a few on Netflix if you have it that all tie together, Jessica Jones, Iron Fist, and Luke Cage.
I will. Thank you for all your knowledge on the movie
Not a problem, it was good talking to you.
Thanks again. It has been nice chatting with you.

uid2response.feedback: I think I will check out this movie
